              <span id="reviewTextContainer2714362089" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10880680789088182141">Just wonderful! So much drama and mystery in this book. Rowland describes her scenes in such excellent detail...whether she is writing about a street scene, a battle, or nature I marvel at her word choices. <br/><br/>Although quite violent (it is about samurais) it was a terrific read. Can&apos;t wait to read the rest of the series!</span>
  <span id="freeText10880680789088182141" style="display:none">Just wonderful! So much drama and mystery in this book. Rowland describes her scenes in such excellent detail...whether she is writing about a street scene, a battle, or nature I marvel at her word choices. <br /><br />Although quite violent (it is about samurais) it was a terrific read. Can't wait to read the rest of the series!</span>
  <a data-text-id="10880680789088182141" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


